| [G-VS2 GIA](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/29090694?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | $3,240 | 10/10. The $10 Twin. Functionally identical to the floor stone. Both are the most efficient G-VS2 entries in the current {{month_year}} market. |
