| [G-VS2 GIA](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/28941971?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | $3,490 | 9/10. The Mid-Premium. At $260 above the VS2 floor, this stone is overlapping F-VS2 territory in price. The $260 premium is almost entirely proportion quality, not clarity. |
